title: docker_deployer.sh
content:
#!/bin/bash

hostnamectl set-hostname docker-backend

apt update && apt upgrade -y && apt install docker.io -y

gpasswd -a ubuntu docker

docker run -d -p 8000:80 --name test.cloudapp.mooo.com ubuntu/apache2

reboot
